<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.10.1">
<l>vaṇṭārpū māmalar maṅkai maṇanōkkam</l>
<l>uṇṭāṉē yuṉṉai yukantukan tuṉṟaṉakkē</l>
<l>toṇṭāṉēṟ keṉceykiṉ ṟāycollu nālvētam</l>
<l>kaṇṭāṉē kaṇṇa purattuṟai yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who enjoys the romantic glances of the lady</l>
<l rend="indent">on a great, blossoming flower full of bees,</l>
<l>What are you doing to me who became a slave to only you,</l>
<l>Yearning and yearning for you? O One who appears in the four Vedas,</l>
<l>Tell [me], lord who dwells in Kaṇṇapuram!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
